{"tid":1233362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【龍和】 大 家 靜 觀 其 變","createTime":"2019-06-16T18:27:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T18:43:46.000Z","uid":154486,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e7ad6bccac20aba63d94a8fe93d215e8f0622223","tid":1233362,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:27:04.000Z","msg":"起水馬ok<br />\n龍和道&hellip; 好柒但係我算<br />\n但係一郁手就唔駛諗一定唔係同路人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果佢地真係鬼，自己打自己<br />\n而家有咁多個鏡頭對住好難做得出乜野<br />\n大家冷靜"},{"pid":"119b7443be40741fd12fae65ab6835ee6210fda1","tid":1233362,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:27:41.000Z","msg":"佢哋有冇戴口罩？"},{"pid":"cdeecaa0137c632adbb8f63154a5c0ad79a8c17e","tid":1233362,"uid":143210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:27:54.000Z","msg":"而家係和理非嘅回合！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1233067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1233067</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唱歌嘅時候就係夜晚<br />\n<br />\n衝嘅時候就係日頭"},{"pid":"2a93f11444d88deb1e23cc08c261573ec4f407e5","tid":1233362,"uid":105694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:27:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日出東方再算"},{"pid":"fa492fdba3f777b6ccb4be64128af7ab00f1dfe0","tid":1233362,"uid":255744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:28:13.000Z","msg":"點解又要封路？<br />\n英國旗婆婆出現"},{"pid":"ff9ba5ea6d77d8c9f2d1c7521575483ebaec9ce7","tid":1233362,"uid":226955,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:31:08.000Z","msg":"係咪有人比鬼引導咗？<br />\n<br />\n其實我唔係太明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解要搞龍和道？可唔可以答我究竟為咗啲乜？政府又唔係話聽日會審逃犯條例，之前一哥都有講「一個冇人冇開會嘅立法會你衝嚟有乜意義姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」，而且龍和道本身易攻難守已經係常識<br />\n<br />\n最重要嘅一點，如果龍和道真係發生衝突，會直接連累埋夏愨道嘅人，參考612嗰日，處於「不反對通知書」區域嘅民陣大台都比黑警狂扔催淚彈，如果龍和道真係打起上嚟，黑警幾乎一定會通殺埋夏愨道嘅人，即使嗰班人係乜都冇做過<br />\n<br />\n所以，真係唔好諗住動武，可能會有鬼想煽動你出手，然後黑警就可以即刻通殺你所有人，聽鄺仔講，唔好有人再受傷，唔好有人再流血，你嘅一小個決定足以救全家或者害全家"},{"pid":"de0acd08612e03149c192a64723e303b30d461f1","tid":1233362,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:31:36.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n而家真係越睇越鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67cc15bc93b012ad4151779904b20d082ed63962","tid":1233362,"uid":157522,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:31:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆不篤灰</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c97b7fcc1644fa786190073c103809c6d5b9ab05","tid":1233362,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67cc15bc93b012ad4151779904b20d082ed63962","tid":1233362,"uid":157522,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:31:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆不篤灰</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:36:27.000Z","msg":"Okok&hellip;<br />\n其實我當年發夢都係咁比人話鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係而家個勢搞唔起呀<br />\n差佬又有異動"},{"pid":"46a88b6891a7e6783c8a41beef3060487ba39337","tid":1233362,"uid":43560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:37:18.000Z","msg":"咪撚衝呀 d狗抖咗大半日 大把精力同你玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58629ec1f52bd4c491992997bb41361fb8f1f05b","tid":1233362,"uid":86383,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:39:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n衝與唔衝，做與唔做<br />\n自己決定，自己承擔<br />\n同為義士，祝你成功<br />\n篤灰割蓆，絕對不做</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"480b4b5ac175bd0859251059dff2443dcddd257c","tid":1233362,"uid":157522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c97b7fcc1644fa786190073c103809c6d5b9ab05","tid":1233362,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor